{"tid":1340394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我住元朗，但我好支持滅撚柒左佢","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:25:55.000Z","uid":130695,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39cb1683830f10ff6d9e602522369cfd50c89c3a","tid":1340394,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:57:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母睇到我扯撚哂火，檯都俾我拍撚爛埋<br />\n今日遊行老婆拗柴陪左佢返屋企睇鐵打<br />\n過一陣就西鐵站暴動<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母黑警特登拖時間仲夾好一人一邊出入<br />\n你估大家無眼睇?<br />\n仲要兩隻軍裝狗睇住都唔做野"},{"pid":"4002bb757d4118b37ed8b7eb8e53020a8b4d5c4a","tid":1340394,"uid":130695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"滅撚左元朗佢啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"08e9bfffd7fa6f6fbfc2c4feedd4df1c2ad85776","tid":1340394,"uid":227706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"我屌佢老母，727拆佢母祠堂"},{"pid":"92bd7a83771958a2a1d6da1757785188bed3fd23","tid":1340394,"uid":283136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08e9bfffd7fa6f6fbfc2c4feedd4df1c2ad85776","tid":1340394,"uid":227706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"我屌佢老母，727拆佢母祠堂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:05:17.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adafe91b79fb7cc1a64de5b70c2777c400c51f8f","tid":1340394,"uid":130695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"08e9bfffd7fa6f6fbfc2c4feedd4df1c2ad85776","tid":1340394,"uid":227706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"我屌佢老母，727拆佢母祠堂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，啱啱我差啲入廚房再出黎<br />\n我老婆喊哂口禁撚住我<br />\n上次遊行已經打電話喊住要我安全返屋企<br />\n依家佢同老母守撚住我係房<br />\n<br />\n但係我真係好撚嬲呀<br />\n屌你老母閪<br />\n警黑合作係咪大撚哂"},{"pid":"51c8156eca39c9c7abba7a5818fa207c15604c47","tid":1340394,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"係咪27號呀，我聽日就想開鳩班仆街波啦"},{"pid":"c1e834edd7f87c17